page.title: 16KEMBLE RAILWAY STATION
page.content: People travel from all over the country to take pictures and film { {Kemble Station.}Once an American tourist offered to buy it and ship it home! Many people bring their friends to look around its attractive gardens and admire its architecture and decorations. It must be the only station to actually get presents from passengers, many of whom by-pass other stations just so they can travel from{Kemble. } Even though they get their daily rush of over 100{London}bound commuters, the staff take their time to listen to people's news and hear a joke.
